name: The Empire's Back (V)
Lore: '''No star system will dare oppose the Emperor now.''',
Text: 'Use 1 Force to deploy (or retrieve) Motti, Tagge, Tarkin, or Vader from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Once during your control phase, for each battleground controlled by Motti, Tagge, Tarkin, or Vader, opponent loses 1 Force.',
